def productExceptSelf(nums):
    n = len(nums)
    output = [1] / n
    left_product = 1
    right_product = 1
    for i in range(n):
        output[i] *= left_product
        left_product *= nums[i]
        output[n - 1 - i] *= right_product
        right_product *= nums[n - 1 - i]
    return output
